		NI DAQ Analog IO
		----------------

Experiments and MatLab code for Reflectance Confocal Microscope (RCM),
both Fiber Scanner system and Galvo system.

National Instruments USB-6211:
   "16-input, 16-bit  250 kS/s Multifunction IO"

Git for Windows:  https://gitforwindows.org/

